      "writtenOn": "2018-10-31T04:03:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Is the idea that stagingFramebuffer is alloced by convert_frame_* and then freed by the caller of convert? What if it was a fixed std::vector living in the camera service that gets resized as we go along, and not have to expose this to the user?",
